title: 2016 Wild Card review
itunes:title: 2016 Wild Card review
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling and Gregg Rosenthal – recap all the action from Wild Card Weekend which included the first career start for Raiders rookie quarterback Conor Cook, and a dominating 4-touchdown performance from Packers quarterback Aaron Rodgers.
